    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a concours-level E46 M3, a definitive masterclass in atmospheric induction. Under the hood lies the S54B32 straight-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS to achieve a linear power band culminating at an 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen boasts a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox, ensuring tactile engagement. Performance is bolstered by a mechanical limited-slip differential and a reinforced rear subframe to mitigate known chassis fatigue. Meticulously maintained with documented rod bearing service and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, the vehicle exhibits zero mechanical lash. The exterior retains its factory luster with original paint depth, while the cabin shows no bolster wear or pixel degradation. A rare, investment-grade example of the ultimate driving machine.",
